#: catalog/templates/catalog/certificacion_industria_detail.html:48
msgid ""
"After checkout you will have access to the material and exam. On passing you "
"will receive your diploma."
msgstr ""
"Después del pago tendrás acceso al material y al examen. Al aprobar "
"recibirás tu diploma."

#: catalog/templates/catalog/certificacion_industria_detail.html:59
msgid ""
"<strong>Paid access.</strong> To view the study material and take the "
"certified exam you must purchase access to this certification. The diploma "
"you receive on passing certifies industry knowledge endorsement, not just "
"course completion."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Acceso de pago.</strong> Para ver el material de estudio y realizar "
"el examen certificado debes comprar acceso a esta certificación. El diploma "
"que recibes al aprobar certifica avalación de conocimientos por la "
"industria, no solo completitud de curso."

#: catalog/templates/catalog/certificacion_industria_detail.html:62
