#: catalog/templates/catalog/certificaciones_industria_list.html:18
msgid ""
"Professionally endorsed industry certifications (cybersecurity, AI, "
"DevSecOps, etc.). They include study material and a 40-question certified "
"exam. <strong>Access to material and exam requires payment.</strong> On "
"passing you receive a diploma certifying knowledge endorsement (not just "
"course completion)."
msgstr ""
"Certificaciones profesionales avaladas por la industria (ciberseguridad, IA, "
"DevSecOps, etc.). Incluyen material de estudio y un examen certificado de 40 "
"preguntas. <strong>El acceso al material y al examen requiere pago.</strong> "
"Al aprobar recibes un diploma que certifica avalación de conocimientos (no "
"solo completitud de curso)."

#: catalog/templates/catalog/certificaciones_industria_list.html:37
msgid "Material + 40-question exam · Diploma on pass"
